  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个物流数据流的流程图，核心是车队管理（FleetManagement）作为数据源，然后经过配送路线（DeliveryRoute）的数据摄取和验证。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，FleetManagement作为起点，数据流向DeliveryRoute进行摄取。那摄取之后需要做什么样的验证？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "INGEST",
        "RAWVAL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "摄取后要做原始数据验证（RAWVAL），通过的话进入处理节点，失败的话要终止并进入仓库的异常处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RAWVAL",
        "PROCESS",
        "STOP",
        "Logistics_Warehouse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把RAWVAL画成判断节点，PASS分支连到PROCESS，FAIL分支连到STOP。STOP节点我先用默认样式，后面再调整？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RAWVAL",
        "PROCESS",
        "STOP"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，STOP确实需要醒目一点，后面标成红色。继续往下，PROCESS处理完之后还要做一次处理结果验证PROCVAL。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PROCESS",
        "PROCVAL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "PROCVAL也是判断节点对吧？VALID和INVALID两个出口分别去哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PROCVAL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "VALID走CONSUME，就是数据最终被消费使用；INVALID走SAFE，进入安全存储或者隔离区，这两个都在Warehouse里。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PROCVAL",
        "CONSUME",
        "SAFE",
        "Logistics_Warehouse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了，CONSUME和SAFE都指向Logistics_Warehouse。现在回到样式，STOP用红色填充，SAFE用黄色警告色可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "STOP",
        "SAFE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，STOP是#ffdddd配深红边框，SAFE用#fff2cc配棕黄边框，这样视觉上能区分异常终止和安全隔离。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "STOP",
        "SAFE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "样式已应用。我检查一下整体结构：FleetManagement → INGEST → RAWVAL判断 → PROCESS → PROCVAL判断 → 最终消费或安全隔离。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "INGEST",
        "RAWVAL",
        "PROCESS",
        "PROCVAL",
        "CONSUME",
        "SAFE"
