      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "现在对了。另外确认一下，PROCESS和PROCVAL的承载主体——PROCESS是DeliveryRoute的处理，PROCVAL验证后进入Warehouse的消费或安全存储。",
